desc: Experience the future of camping. The all-new Skycamp rooftop tent allows you to travel and camp anywhere you can drive. Set up your premium-quality king-sized tent in less than 1 minute. A Kickstarter record-breaker, the Skycamp is the industry's leading rooftop tent—straddling the line between luxury and ruggedness.

layout.text: Imagine a full camping experience that can fit into a sleek hardshell on top of your roof.
